 	<li><a href="https://emergencemagazine.org/essay/telling-the-bees/" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">Emily Polk considers bees and grief</span></a></li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2025/04/14/sayaka-muratas-alien-eye" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">Elif Batuman profiles Sayaka Murata</span></a></li>
